==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Demantoid
<hw>De*man"toid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G.
<ets>demant</ets> diamond + <ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
<def>A yellow-green, transparent variety of garnet found in the Urals.
It is valued as a gem because of its brilliancy of luster, whence the
name.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

